        "question": "In the course of pilgrimage, Emperor Ashoka visited the following places. Which route did he follow ? Select the correct answer from the codes given below: 1. Gaya 2. Kapilavastu 3. Kushinagar 4. Lumbini 5. Sarnath 6. Shravasti Code:",
